---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Walkway Planks Buyer's Guide | Prime Steel Tech">
<main class="bg-[#2b332a] min-h-screen pt-20 text-zinc-300">
<section class="py-16 sm:py-24 border-b border-white/5 relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-emerald-500/10 blur-[120px] rounded-full"></div>
<div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
<div><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1541888946425-d81bb19240f5?q=80&w=1600" class="w-full rounded-sm border border-white/10" /></div>
<div>
<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-emerald-500/30 bg-emerald-500/5 px-4 py-2 text-[11px] font-semibold text-emerald-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">Buyer's Guide</div>
<h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black text-white uppercase tracking-tight mb-6 leading-[1.1]">What are <span class="text-emerald-400">Walkway Planks?</span></h1>
<p class="font-jakarta text-zinc-300 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">Steel Walkway Planks are safe working platforms used in scaffolding systems for construction and industrial access. Manufactured from IS 2062 Grade E250 steel with anti-slip perforated surfaces, they provide excellent grip, durability and corrosion resistance.</p>
<p class="font-jakarta text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Compatible with Ringlock, Cuplock, Tube-and-Coupler and Frame Scaffolding systems.</p>

            <div class="flex mt-8">
              <a href="/pdfs/Walkway-Buyers-Guide.pdf" download class="group inline-flex h-12 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-[3px] bg-emerald-500 px-8 text-[13px] font-bold text-[#050f09] uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-emerald-400 transition-colors shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(16,185,129,0.2)]">
                <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4"/></svg>
                DOWNLOAD BUYER'S GUIDE
              </a>
            </div>

</div></div></div></section>
<section class="py-16 bg-[#262d25]"><div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4"><h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white uppercase text-center mb-10">Why Steel Walkway Planks are Better than <span class="text-emerald-400">Traditional Wooden Planks</span></h2><div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-sm p-8"><p class="font-jakarta text-zinc-300 leading-loose">Steel walkway planks offer superior safety, anti-slip performance, corrosion resistance and longer service life than wooden planks. They do not warp, crack or absorb moisture and are ideal for industrial environments.</p></div></div></section>
<section class="py-16"><div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4">
  <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white uppercase mb-8">Technical <span class="text-emerald-400">Specifications</span></h2>
  <div class="overflow-auto rounded-sm border border-white/10 bg-zinc-900/50">
    <table class="w-full font-jakarta text-sm">
      <thead><tr class="bg-emerald-900/60 border-b border-white/10">
        <th class="px-6 py-4 text-left font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wider">Parameter</th>
        <th class="px-6 py-4 text-left font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wider">Specification</th>
      </tr></thead>
      <tbody class="divide-y divide-white/5 text-zinc-300">
        <tr class="hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors"><td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-white">Steel Grade</td><td class="px-6 py-4">IS 2062 E250</td></tr>
        <tr class="hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors"><td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-white">Deck Thickness</td><td class="px-6 py-4">14/16 Gauge — 2 mm / 1.6 mm</td></tr>
        <tr class="hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors"><td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-white">Board Width</td><td class="px-6 py-4">300 / 280 / 240 mm</td></tr>
        <tr class="hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors"><td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-white">Board Lengths</td><td class="px-6 py-4">1250 / 2000 / 2500 / 3000 mm · Custom on request</td></tr>
        <tr class="hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors"><td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-white">Galvanising</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Min 45 µm zinc · Pre Galvanised · EN ISO 1461</td></tr>
        <tr class="hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors"><td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-white">Welding</td><td class="px-6 py-4">MIG/MAG · IS 816</td></tr>
        <tr class="hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors"><td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-white">Stiffener Spacing</td><td class="px-6 py-4">500 mm c/c transverse · Longitudinal added when width &gt; 400 mm</td></tr>
        <tr class="hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors"><td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-white">Safety Factor</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Min 4× intended load</td></tr>
        <tr class="hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors"><td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-white">Deflection Limit</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Span / 60</td></tr>
        <tr class="hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors"><td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-white">Max Plank Gap</td><td class="px-6 py-4">25 mm</td></tr>
        <tr class="hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors"><td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-white">Overhang</td><td class="px-6 py-4">50 mm min / 150 mm max</td></tr>
        <tr class="hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors"><td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-white">Service Life</td><td class="px-6 py-4">8–15 years outdoor / industrial</td></tr>
        <tr class="hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors"><td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-white">Compatible Systems</td><td class="px-6 py-4">Tube-and-Coupler · Cuplock · Frame Scaffold · Ringlock</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</div></section>

<section class="py-16 bg-[#262d25]"><div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4">
  <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white uppercase mb-8">Available <span class="text-emerald-400">Walkway Plank Types</span></h2>
  <div class="overflow-auto rounded-sm border border-white/10 bg-zinc-900/50">
    <table class="w-full font-jakarta text-sm">
      <thead><tr class="bg-emerald-900/60 border-b border-white/10">
        <th class="px-6 py-4 text-left font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wider">Surface Type</th>
        <th class="px-6 py-4 text-center font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wider">Availability</th>
        <th class="px-6 py-4 text-center font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wider">Deck Type</th>
        <th class="px-6 py-4 text-center font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wider">Drainage</th>
        <th class="px-6 py-4 text-left font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wider">Best For</th>
      </tr></thead>
      <tbody class="divide-y divide-white/5 text-zinc-300">
        <tr class="hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors">
          <td class="px-6 py-5">
            <span class="block font-bold text-white">Antiskid Dimple Plate</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-0.5 block">Hemispherical cold-pressed dimples with round perforations</span>
          </td>
          <td class="px-6 py-5 text-center"><span class="px-2.5 py-1 bg-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-400 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest rounded-sm">Standard</span></td>
          <td class="px-6 py-5 text-center text-zinc-400">Perforated</td>
          <td class="px-6 py-5 text-center text-zinc-400">Omnidirectional</td>
          <td class="px-6 py-5 text-zinc-400">General scaffolding platforms, construction sites</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors">
          <td class="px-6 py-5">
            <span class="block font-bold text-white">Diamond Checker Plate</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-0.5 block">Diamond-pattern embossed anti-slip surface</span>
          </td>
          <td class="px-6 py-5 text-center"><span class="px-2.5 py-1 bg-zinc-700/60 text-zinc-300 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest rounded-sm">On Request</span></td>
          <td class="px-6 py-5 text-center text-zinc-400">Solid</td>
          <td class="px-6 py-5 text-center text-zinc-400">Longitudinal &amp; transverse</td>
          <td class="px-6 py-5 text-zinc-400">Stair towers, access walkways, high-traffic areas</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors">
          <td class="px-6 py-5">
            <span class="block font-bold text-white">Checker Plate</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-0.5 block">Parallel raised ribs with linear drainage channels</span>
          </td>
          <td class="px-6 py-5 text-center"><span class="px-2.5 py-1 bg-zinc-700/60 text-zinc-300 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest rounded-sm">On Request</span></td>
          <td class="px-6 py-5 text-center text-zinc-400">Solid</td>
          <td class="px-6 py-5 text-center text-zinc-400">Directional (channel)</td>
          <td class="px-6 py-5 text-zinc-400">Oil &amp; gas plants, food-processing walkways</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
  <p class="font-jakarta text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-4">All types available in widths 240 / 280 / 300 mm and lengths 1250 / 2000 / 2500 / 3000 mm. Custom lengths on request.</p>
</div></section>

<section class="py-16 bg-[#2b332a]"><div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4"><h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white uppercase text-center mb-12">Factors to Consider Before Buying <span class="text-emerald-400">Walkway Planks</span></h2><div class="space-y-6"><div class="bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-sm border border-white/10"><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 uppercase">01. Surface Grip</h3><p class="font-jakarta text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Choose anti-slip perforated surfaces for safe footing in all weather conditions. Antiskid Dimple Plate is the standard choice for most scaffolding applications.</p></div><div class="bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-sm border border-white/10"><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 uppercase">02. Load Capacity</h3><p class="font-jakarta text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Select planks with adequate safe working load for your platform. All Prime Steeltech planks carry a minimum 4× safety factor over intended load with deflection capped at Span/60.</p></div><div class="bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-sm border border-white/10"><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 uppercase">03. Corrosion Resistance</h3><p class="font-jakarta text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Hot-dip galvanised planks with min 45 µm zinc coating ensure 8–15 years outdoor service life. Critical for coastal, chemical and industrial environments.</p></div><div class="bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-sm border border-white/10"><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 uppercase">04. Compliance</h3><p class="font-jakarta text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Choose planks complying with IS 3696, IS 4014 and EN ISO 1461. All Prime Steeltech walkway planks are manufactured to IS 2062 E250 with MIG/MAG welding per IS 816.</p></div></div></div></section>

</main></Layout>
<style is:global>@import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap"); .font-jakarta{font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;}</style>